{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"50fe8ccb77","title":"给妻子丁一岚的遗书","origin":"袁鹰《玉碎》，载沈展云、梁以墀、李行远编《中国知识分子悲欢录》，广州：花城出版社1993年8月第一版。","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"a301b136a6","index":0,"year":1966,"month":5,"day":17,"articleId":"50fe8ccb77"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"GPCRv3","name":"中国文化大革命文库（第三版）","internal":true,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"5dbdbb510d","name":"邓拓"}]},"publication_details":{"GPCRv3":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a3ca9cdbd2","type":"title","text":"给妻子丁一岚的遗书","index":0,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"50fe8ccb77"},{"id":"910854395d","type":"authors","text":"邓拓","index":1,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"50fe8ccb77"},{"id":"0490c281e9","type":"paragraph","text":"我因为赶写了一封长信给市委，来不及给你们写信。此刻心脏跳动很不规律，肠疾又在纠缠，不多写了。","index":2,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"50fe8ccb77"},{"id":"29986f3576","type":"paragraph","text":"你们永远不要想起我，永远忘掉我吧。我害得你们够苦了，今后你们永远解除了我所给予你们的精神创伤。","index":3,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"50fe8ccb77"},{"id":"63a7158374","type":"paragraph","text":"永别了，亲爱的。","index":4,"publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"50fe8ccb77"}],"page":{"id":"f999bb0b92","publicationId":"GPCRv3","articleId":"50fe8ccb77","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}